        <p style="margin:0 0 6px;color:rgba(201,169,110,0.7);font-weight:600;">Privacy Policy</p>
        <p style="margin:0;color:rgba(240,237,228,0.4);">* Personal information you provide (name, email, phone number, etc.) will be used solely for reservation confirmation, communication, and store notifications. We will not share your information with third parties except as required by law.</p>
